    • Field Detail

      • ELEMENT_WAITING_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties ELEMENT_WAITING_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for some web elements are present and suit some criteria. When "WAITING_FOR_ELEMENTS_TIME_UNIT" or "WAITING_FOR_ELEMENTS_TIME" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.

      • WAITING_ALERT_TIME_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties WAITING_ALERT_TIME_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for appearance of an alert. When "WAITING_FOR_ALERTS_TIME_UNIT" or "WAITING_FOR_ALERTS_TIME" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.

      • WAITING_WINDOW_TIME_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties WAITING_WINDOW_TIME_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for some window. When "WAITING_FOR_WINDOWS_TIME_UNIT" or "WAITING_FOR_WINDOWS_TIME" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.

      • WAITING_FRAME_SWITCHING_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties WAITING_FRAME_SWITCHING_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for the switching to some frame succeeded. When "WAITING_FOR_FRAME_SWITCHING_TIME_UNIT" or "WAITING_FOR_FRAME_SWITCHING_TIME" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.

      • WAITING_FOR_PAGE_LOADED_DURATION

        public static final WaitingProperties WAITING_FOR_PAGE_LOADED_DURATION
        Returns duration of the waiting for waiting for a page is loaded. When "WAITING_FOR_PAGE_LOADED_TIME_UNIT" or "WAITING_FOR_PAGE_LOADED_TIME" are not defined then it returns 1 minute. Otherwise it returns defined duration value.
